* {{Citation |last=Hessayon |first=D.G. |year=1999 |title=The Bulb Expert |publication-place=London|publisher=Transworld Publishers Ltd |isbn=978-0-903505-42-0 }} &lt;!-- &lt;ref name=&quot;Hessayon_1999&quot;&gt;{{Harvnb|Hessayon|1999}}&lt;/ref&gt; --&gt;
* {{Citation |last=Hilu |first=K. |last2=Borsch |first2=T. |last3=Muller |first3=K. |last4=Soltis|first4=D.E. |coauthors=Soltis, P.S.; Savolainen, V.; Chase, M.W.; Powell, M.P.; Alice, L.A.; Evans, R.; Sauquet, H.; Neinhuis, C.; Slotta, T.A.B.; Rohwer, J.G.; Campbell, C. S. &amp; Chatrou, L.W. |year=2003 |title=Angiosperm phylogeny based on ''matK'' sequence information |journal=American J. Bot. |volume=90|pages=1758–1766|url=http://www.amjbot.org/cgi/content/full/90/12/1758 |accessdate=2010-12-20 }} &lt;!-- &lt;ref name=&quot;Hilu_Borsch_Muller_Soltis_2003&quot;&gt;{{Harvnb|Hilu|Borsch|Muller|Soltis|2003}}&lt;/ref&gt; --&gt;
