* W. S. Judd, C. S. Campbell, E. A. Kellogg, P. F. Stevens, M. J. Donoghue,  2002. Plant Systematics: A Phylogenetic Approach, 2nd edition.  Sinauer Associates,  Sunderland, Massachusetts ISBN 0-87893-403-0.

